{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2752020/extras/steambarsstone4.png?t=1734743452\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2752020/extras/combat.gif?t=1734743452\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage in challenging tactical combat involving the use of dozens of available abilities. Each party member brings with them different specialties and it's up to you how to combine them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2752020/extras/steambarsstone5.png?t=1734743452\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2752020/extras/TownGrowth.gif?t=1734743452\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Explore a world filled with dungeons, npcs and towns to explore. As you progress into each storyline new quests and buildings unlock providing further progression paths. The more the world grows, the more npcs and quests are unlocked and the further you can progress with new quests and new clues on further areas to discover, all which is reflected visually in the world.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2752020/extras/steambarsstone3.png?t=1734743452\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2752020/extras/BuildingTown.gif?t=1734743452\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A non linear story that allows you to progress the way you wish. The world is filled with both quests and dungeons big and small, from small monster caves to multi floored mega dungeons there is a variety of things to do and discover. All locations are hand crafted, no procedural generation. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2752020/extras/steambarsstone1.png?t=1734743452\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2752020/extras/Steamplayers.gif?t=1734743452\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> There are a variety of different premade npcs to choose from or for those who prefer to create their entire parties, you can completely customise your party members with a deep character creator including all skills, classes, combat sprites and character portraits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2752020/extras/Portrait.gif?t=1734743452\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2752020/extras/steambarsstone2.png?t=1734743452\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">* A large open world to explore in your own way, at your own pace with dozen of handcrafted dungeon locations. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">* Assemble a party of customisable characters each with their own combat and non combat skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">* Fight 100s of different enemies each with their own unique abilities in turn based combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p cl